<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>日本都道府県別人口ヒートマップ</title>
  <script src="https://d3js.org/d3.v7.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", "Yu Gothic", "Meiryo", sans-serif;
      background: #1a1a2e;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: #a8d8ea;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    #controls {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    #controls label {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #ccc;
    }

    #yearSelect {
      padding: 6px 12px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      border: 1px solid #4a6fa5;
      background: #16213e;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    #yearSelect:focus {
      outline: 2px solid #a8d8ea;
    }

    #map-container {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 960px;
    }

    svg {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }

    .prefecture {
      stroke: #2a2a4a;
      stroke-width: 0.5;
      transition: opacity 0.15s;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .prefecture:hover {
      opacity: 0.75;
      stroke: #ffffff;
      stroke-width: 1.2;
    }

    #tooltip {
      position: fixed;
      background: rgba(22, 33, 62, 0.95);
      border: 1px solid #4a6fa5;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.1s;
      z-index: 100;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    #tooltip .name {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #a8d8ea;
    }

    #tooltip .pop {
      color: #e0e0e0;
    }

    #legend-container {
      margin-top: 12px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    #legend-container span {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #aaa;
    }

    #source {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>🗾 日本都道府県別人口ヒートマップ</h1>

  <div id="controls">
    <label for="yearSelect">表示年：</label>
    <select id="yearSelect"></select>
  </div>

  <div id="map-container">
    <svg id="map" viewBox="0 0 960 600" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"></svg>
  </div>

  <div id="legend-container">
    <svg id="legend" width="360" height="50"></svg>
    <span>人口（万人）</span>
  </div>

  <div id="tooltip"></div>

  <p id="source">データ出典: e-Stat 政府統計の総合窓口（国勢調査）</p>

